---
title: Mapo Tofu
tags: quick and easy, tofu
servings: 3
cook time: 10 minutes
ai_image: true
date added: 2026-03-21
---

Cut @tofu{1%block} into 1-inch cubes. Brown @ground beef{1/4%lb} in a #skillet{} over medium heat with @onion{1/2%small} (diced). Drain any excess fat. Add @House Foods Mapo Tofu Sauce{1%packet}, the tofu cubes, and @frozen peas{1/2%cup}. Gently stir to coat. Simmer for ~{5%minutes} until heated through. Serve over @steamed rice{}.
